                                                                                              Closely related to, and a part of security and privacy risks, supply chain risk 8 is also of growing
                                                                                              concern to organizations. Because of the increased reliance on third-party or external providers
                                                                                              and commercial-off-the-shelf products, systems, and services, attacks or disruptions in the
                                                                                              supply chain which impact an organization’s systems are increasing. Such attacks can be difficult
